2
00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:34.450
My Bible

3
00:01:34.450 --> 00:01:36.700
Big Sis! Stay with me!

4
00:01:38.130 --> 00:01:39.120
Big Sis!

5
00:01:39.870 --> 00:01:41.580
Hey, dumbasses!

6
00:01:41.580 --> 00:01:43.580
Fetch the medics!

7
00:01:46.450 --> 00:01:47.170
Hey!

8
00:01:47.170 --> 00:01:47.940
Sir!

9
00:01:48.920 --> 00:01:53.890
Find those two, corner them,
then summon the rest of us.

10
00:01:56.850 --> 00:01:59.200
Yamato, you bastard...

11
00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.850
Page One!

12
00:02:00.850 --> 00:02:03.510
You took a pretty nasty hit too.

13
00:02:04.490 --> 00:02:06.900
Yeah, that was quite the punch...

14
00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:08.850
Think he dislocated my jaw.

15
00:02:08.850 --> 00:02:10.230
That's all?!

16
00:02:10.650 --> 00:02:13.660
More importantly, where are the medics?

17
00:02:13.660 --> 00:02:15.910
We're here!

18
00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:29.130
You're hurting my eyes!

19
00:02:34.550 --> 00:02:36.760
Pay-Pay!

20
00:02:38.600 --> 00:02:40.560
It hurts ever so much!

21
00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:43.350
Poor sweet little me!

22
00:02:43.350 --> 00:02:45.560
Maybe you should pipe down then?

23
00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:47.390
What did you say?!

24
00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:49.230
Are you trying to make me cry?!

25
00:02:54.530 --> 00:02:56.900
That lousy Yamato!

26
00:02:56.900 --> 00:03:00.910
How dare he steal
Viceroy Kaido's Thunder Bagua?!

27
00:03:00.910 --> 00:03:02.500
She's fine all right.

28
00:03:03.670 --> 00:03:06.040
His is more like Blunder Bagua.

29
00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:12.140
It didn't even hurt...

30
00:03:12.140 --> 00:03:13.460
Big Sis...

31
00:03:13.460 --> 00:03:14.800
Master Page One!

32
00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:17.300
Young Master Yamato
and Straw Hat have stopped!

33
00:03:17.300 --> 00:03:18.340
Okay!

34
00:03:19.780 --> 00:03:21.430
Hey, Pay-Pay!

35
00:03:22.820 --> 00:03:25.810
Don't leave me!

36
00:03:28.600 --> 00:03:30.480
Where are you taking me?!

37
00:03:30.480 --> 00:03:33.070
I don't have time for strangers!

38
00:03:33.070 --> 00:03:34.490
Please wait.

39
00:03:34.490 --> 00:03:36.700
I merely wish to speak.

40
00:03:37.880 --> 00:03:39.440
Get out of my way!

41
00:03:53.770 --> 00:03:55.470
Listen to what I have to say!

42
00:04:09.980 --> 00:04:11.650
You have five seconds!

43
00:04:20.190 --> 00:04:21.620
People can hear us.

44
00:04:21.620 --> 00:04:23.160
Let's speak in private.

45
00:04:24.490 --> 00:04:26.000
Then forget it!

46
00:04:32.250 --> 00:04:34.210
Gum-Gum...

47
00:04:34.210 --> 00:04:36.420
Gatling!

48
00:04:52.090 --> 00:04:53.230
You stubborn jerk!

49
00:04:55.340 --> 00:04:57.690
Red Hawk!

50
00:05:06.820 --> 00:05:08.170
This reminds me of...

51
00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:11.670
my battle against him!

52
00:05:19.050 --> 00:05:20.300
Damn!

53
00:05:20.300 --> 00:05:21.430
They're gone!

54
00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:22.970
What's going on?

55
00:05:22.970 --> 00:05:24.300
Where's Yamato?

56
00:05:24.740 --> 00:05:25.720
I'm sorry!

57
00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:28.020
We lost them both!

