508
00:23:00.440 --> 00:23:07.820
Kikunojo of the Lingering Snow
A Retainer of the Kozuki Clan

509
00:23:00.690 --> 00:23:05.980
Like the snow that remains in spring, so, too,
shall they torment your soul forevermore!

510
00:23:11.660 --> 00:23:12.870
Come at me, Kiku!

511
00:23:27.510 --> 00:23:30.640
Hey! Turn on the video
transponder snail already!

512
00:23:30.640 --> 00:23:33.730
Kaido's speech has started!

513
00:23:34.600 --> 00:23:37.850
I, as Kozuki Oden, thought that you...

514
00:23:37.850 --> 00:23:43.530
as Ace's brother, would allow me
to board your ship, so I gathered info on you.

515
00:23:43.530 --> 00:23:44.530
Hey!

516
00:23:44.530 --> 00:23:47.530
Everyone loves Kozuki Oden!

517
00:23:47.530 --> 00:23:50.160
You can't just be him!

518
00:23:51.200 --> 00:23:53.540
Fine, you're more Oden than I am!

519
00:23:53.540 --> 00:23:56.120
What do you mean I'm more Oden than you?!

520
00:23:57.420 --> 00:24:00.340
Even if I am Oden, I'm still not free...

521
00:24:02.190 --> 00:24:03.960
because of these cuffs!

522
00:24:07.090 --> 00:24:10.500
I wanted to set out to sea
along with Ace and his crew...

523
00:24:13.140 --> 00:24:17.690
but I've been held captive
on this island since I was eight!

524
00:24:19.600 --> 00:24:21.310
Aren't those for prisoners?

525
00:24:21.310 --> 00:24:22.690
Yes!

526
00:24:22.690 --> 00:24:26.780
My father said they would explode
should I ever leave the island.

527
00:24:27.320 --> 00:24:31.200
Honestly, I think that was probably a lie...

528
00:24:31.200 --> 00:24:34.160
because what kind of a parent
would blow up their own son?!

529
00:24:34.990 --> 00:24:39.170
But when I think of the worst case scenario,
I feel weak at the knees...

530
00:24:39.170 --> 00:24:41.420
because my father is that kind of man.

531
00:24:41.420 --> 00:24:43.170
Want me to take them off?

532
00:24:44.130 --> 00:24:45.010
What?!

533
00:24:45.010 --> 00:24:49.680
Do you really wanna fight alongside us?

534
00:24:49.680 --> 00:24:53.760
If you come with me, I'll be kicking
Kaido's ass right in front of you!

535
00:24:53.760 --> 00:24:56.020
I wish I could do it myself!

536
00:24:56.020 --> 00:25:00.650
I've lost count of the beatings
he's given me since I was a child!

537
00:25:00.650 --> 00:25:03.570
Every time I challenged him, I was defeated!

538
00:25:03.570 --> 00:25:04.570
I see.

539
00:25:04.570 --> 00:25:06.220
Okay, I'll take them off for you!

540
00:25:06.220 --> 00:25:07.740
Take them off?

541
00:25:07.740 --> 00:25:10.820
They've restricted my freedom
for twenty years...

542
00:25:10.820 --> 00:25:12.950
It's not as easy as...

543
00:25:12.950 --> 00:25:16.310
It's been two years since
the Summit War against Whitebeard!

544
00:25:22.130 --> 00:25:25.010
It's footage from the Performance Floor!

545
00:25:27.070 --> 00:25:30.430
The gears of the world are turning once again!

546
00:25:30.430 --> 00:25:35.510
The abolition of the Seven Warlords wasn't
some act of madness by the government!

547
00:25:40.600 --> 00:25:43.350
It's a sign of confidence in their ability

548
00:25:43.350 --> 00:25:47.440
to bring us to heel with new
countermeasures at Marine Headquarters.

549
00:25:51.450 --> 00:25:56.280
But while the World Government
wallows in ignorance,

550
00:25:56.860 --> 00:26:00.020
we will gather the most
powerful forces in this world...

551
00:26:00.020 --> 00:26:02.620
the ancient weapons!

552
00:26:08.170 --> 00:26:10.300
To accomplish that...

553
00:26:19.470 --> 00:26:22.440
we have entered into
an alliance with Big Mom!

554
00:26:38.160 --> 00:26:40.040
Did I hear you...

555
00:26:40.330 --> 00:26:46.670
Olin the Oiran
Captain of the Big Mom Pirates
Bounty: 4 Billion 388 Million Berries

556
00:26:41.160 --> 00:26:44.720
call out my name, Kaido?

557
00:26:53.340 --> 00:26:54.660
Oh, my...

558
00:26:55.510 --> 00:26:56.890
Big Mom?!

559
00:26:59.890 --> 00:27:03.090
Welcome back, Zeus.

560
00:27:03.100 --> 00:27:05.430
Ma... ma...

561
00:27:05.430 --> 00:27:06.230
Mama!

562
00:27:09.610 --> 00:27:12.780
She's terrifying up close!

563
00:27:12.780 --> 00:27:15.610
She's the world's strongest old hag!

564
00:27:20.580 --> 00:27:21.830
Zeus!

565
00:27:22.980 --> 00:27:23.620
Nami!

566
00:27:24.040 --> 00:27:25.670
They were caught?!

567
00:27:27.170 --> 00:27:30.380
You're finally here, Linlin!

568
00:27:30.380 --> 00:27:33.010
What took you so long?!

569
00:27:33.600 --> 00:27:36.840
Don't be such a stickler, Kaido!

570
00:27:36.840 --> 00:27:38.850
I made it in time.

571
00:27:44.180 --> 00:27:46.730
As Kaido said,

572
00:27:46.730 --> 00:27:51.570
we formed an alliance with a purpose in mind!

573
00:27:52.440 --> 00:27:53.690
A purpose?

574
00:27:53.690 --> 00:27:57.030
If we're at each other's throats,
it's out of our reach,

575
00:27:57.030 --> 00:28:00.660
but if we join hands,
it's already within our grasp!

576
00:28:00.660 --> 00:28:02.830
Listen up, you louts!

577
00:28:02.830 --> 00:28:06.460
We're doubling down on piracy!

578
00:28:06.460 --> 00:28:08.670
At long last...

579
00:28:08.670 --> 00:28:11.460
...we're going to claim...

580
00:28:14.090 --> 00:28:17.260
...the great treasure
One Piece!

581
00:28:24.020 --> 00:28:25.390
The One Piece...

582
00:28:25.840 --> 00:28:28.900
What the heck! That's my treasure!

583
00:28:28.900 --> 00:28:31.060
Those jerks!

584
00:28:32.730 --> 00:28:35.740
The fear of the ancient weapons...

585
00:28:35.740 --> 00:28:39.640
will ignite a terrible war across the world!

586
00:28:40.490 --> 00:28:42.490
Prepare yourselves!

587
00:28:42.490 --> 00:28:47.960
That is the violent world that we desire!

588
00:28:54.460 --> 00:28:56.300
How exciting!

589
00:28:58.360 --> 00:29:02.470
Any of you who serve Orochi, listen up!

590
00:29:03.510 --> 00:29:06.470
You've got a choice to make.

591
00:29:08.560 --> 00:29:10.480
A choice?

592
00:29:11.480 --> 00:29:13.440
This country...

593
00:29:13.440 --> 00:29:16.030
is a natural stronghold surrounded by the falls,

594
00:29:16.030 --> 00:29:21.610
which makes it difficult for the Marines
and the World Government to penetrate.

595
00:29:21.610 --> 00:29:24.410
If we build more weapons factories...

596
00:29:26.350 --> 00:29:30.040
and force even the people
of the Flower Capital to work,

597
00:29:30.040 --> 00:29:36.000
this place will become a lawless land,
a paradise for pirates!

598
00:29:41.630 --> 00:29:42.920
Hey...

599
00:29:45.510 --> 00:29:46.560
Hey!

600
00:29:46.950 --> 00:29:49.930
Kaido, you swine!

601
00:29:49.930 --> 00:29:53.060
The Flower Capital is my territory!

602
00:29:57.900 --> 00:29:59.860
Do you hear me?!

603
00:30:01.120 --> 00:30:06.990
For torturing the Kurozumi Clan,
I'll bring those Kozuki devils to their knees

604
00:30:06.990 --> 00:30:12.920
and subject them to all manner of horrors
to keep them from rising up!

605
00:30:12.920 --> 00:30:17.920
Forever and ever!

606
00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:21.010
Wano is mine to destroy!

607
00:30:21.010 --> 00:30:24.660
This country belongs to me!

608
00:30:24.660 --> 00:30:28.430
Know your place, Kaido!

609
00:30:28.430 --> 00:30:30.890
You're not even from here!

610
00:30:30.890 --> 00:30:36.610
Who do you think is making it possible
for you to procure weapons?!

611
00:30:36.610 --> 00:30:39.070
Wano can only exist with me!

612
00:30:39.070 --> 00:30:41.030
Don't you dare forget that!

613
00:30:46.340 --> 00:30:48.450
I see you understand.

614
00:30:48.880 --> 00:30:50.660
What we've got to do now...

615
00:30:50.660 --> 00:30:53.460
is kill that brat immedia–

616
00:31:09.550 --> 00:31:11.140
I don't care!

617
00:31:11.140 --> 00:31:13.850
We don't need him anymore!

618
00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:37.630
Utter tripe!

619
00:31:42.150 --> 00:31:44.010
To me...

620
00:31:48.800 --> 00:31:50.470
both the Kurozumi Clan...

621
00:31:51.220 --> 00:31:53.100
and the Kozuki Clan...

622
00:31:56.190 --> 00:31:58.980
mean nothing!

623
00:32:11.240 --> 00:32:11.870
Momo!

624
00:32:12.380 --> 00:32:14.290
Hey, that's Momo!

625
00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:17.080
Momo, wait for me!

626
00:32:17.080 --> 00:32:18.710
Hey, keep it down!

627
00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:25.260
Hey, what the hell?!

628
00:32:25.260 --> 00:32:26.760
What's going on?!

629
00:32:26.760 --> 00:32:27.930
Huh?

630
00:32:28.930 --> 00:32:32.470
And now the pirate-loving fly is dead.

631
00:32:32.470 --> 00:32:37.060
Those loyal to Orochi
have five seconds to decide!

632
00:32:37.820 --> 00:32:41.020
Become pirates and follow me...

633
00:32:41.410 --> 00:32:44.730
or challenge us right here and die?

634
00:32:45.400 --> 00:32:49.260
To prepare for the coming worldwide war,

635
00:32:49.260 --> 00:32:53.780
I will turn this country into a pirate empire!

636
00:32:55.620 --> 00:32:59.290
We'll ramp up the expeditions
for our primary business.

637
00:33:00.040 --> 00:33:01.000
So tonight,

638
00:33:01.000 --> 00:33:04.380
we will relocate Onigashima
to the Flower Capital,

639
00:33:04.380 --> 00:33:06.670
and Wano will fall!

640
00:33:07.300 --> 00:33:09.010
That bastard!

641
00:33:09.010 --> 00:33:12.760
The country's name will be New Onigashima!

642
00:33:12.760 --> 00:33:15.890
And the new shogun will be my son...

643
00:33:15.890 --> 00:33:17.600
Yamato!

644
00:33:21.060 --> 00:33:22.240
What did he...

645
00:33:23.690 --> 00:33:27.650
just say?!

646
00:33:34.150 --> 00:33:36.540
You can't just force that on me!

647
00:33:36.540 --> 00:33:38.830
You shitty old man!

648
00:33:39.410 --> 00:33:40.330
Hurry up!

649
00:33:40.330 --> 00:33:42.030
They're gonna kill Momo!

650
00:33:42.030 --> 00:33:43.800
I know a shortcut!

651
00:33:43.800 --> 00:33:44.540
Okay!
